{"tid":527369,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"寒風下元朗通宵尋走失狗B　動物義工：只想牠能見狗媽媽最後一面","createTime":"2018-01-12T14:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T07:55:04.000Z","uid":104585,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c4462c7533f809fa9f3cd348daa985097246a58f","tid":527369,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"前兩天氣溫急降兼落雨，人人也想躲在被竇內，但有十多位義工，卻冒着冷雨走到元朗一帶通宵尋狗BB Stanley。<br />\n「Stanley只有8個人大，獲領養翌日卻因狗主大意而走失。義工兩個月來仍每晚落區找牠。」有份一同尋找Stanley的獨立義工Mimi說。<br />\n義工們有個心願，希望Stanley有機會再見生母一面。「狗媽媽由法國家庭領養了，將會移居法國。」然而隨着時間流逝，這個願望似乎愈來愈遠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/222840_14f1b9b60fa5a7044b55947948e819bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F222840_14f1b9b60fa5a7044b55947948e819bf.jpg&h=fbe70919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStanley（右）和狗媽媽（左）原是流浪狗，約一年前被漁護署捉走後，被動物收容所救起。（受訪者提供）<br />\n<br />\n遍尋大半個元朗區 <br />\n<br />\n「狗媽媽似乎也知道兒子出事了，我們領着牠到元朗尋找Stanley，牠也乖乖跟着。」Mimi說。Stanley自 11月10日走失後，曾救起Stanley的動物收容所職員和義工兩天後才從網上得知，錯失48小時黃金搜索時間。但他們仍決定每天到元朗尋犬，Mini見義工們如此辛苦，於是加入尋犬隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n他們搜索範圍之廣令人驚訝，「我們到錦上路、錦田、八鄉、石崗一帶貼街招，我駕車可以去更遠，有時會到荃錦公路、林錦公路貼街招。」街招卻很快被人撕下，於是義工不停再貼上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/222959_be5b8a83b7c98380bda62629f546b925.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F222959_be5b8a83b7c98380bda62629f546b925.jpg&h=3479b148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受傷仍繼續<br />\n<br />\n兩個月連續不斷駕車尋找Stanley，Mimi的右腳因此拉傷，這幾天要稍作休息，但其餘義工仍然努力不懈出動尋犬。<br />\n<br />\n「前兩天只有8度，元朗再低幾度，下着雨，好凍，但義工都不想放棄。我們穿衣服都冷得顫抖，Stanley只是個小孩，而且毛很短，一定很冷了&hellip;」Mimi語帶哽咽地說。<br />\n<br />\nStanley的外表平凡，街坊不免認錯牠：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223159_b16b16f0b7c7967a569c6f546f79050e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223159_b16b16f0b7c7967a569c6f546f79050e.jpg&h=d3f58731&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223200_25bffb2d874d2fb8848d65f4ab1dbdf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223200_25bffb2d874d2fb8848d65f4ab1dbdf3.jpg&h=06b32080&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223201_8b27bd61d4a35e5a3da38044a8236109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223201_8b27bd61d4a35e5a3da38044a8236109.jpg&h=f174487a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街坊熱心打氣<br />\n<br />\n元朗鄉郊的社區連結很強，街坊不只組織網上群組通消息，線下亦會主動打招呼問好。「有街坊見到我們貼街招，會主動走來查問現時情況，有些又會說『我也幫忙留意。』」看似微不足道的說話，卻能為義工打氣。<br />\n<br />\n早前不少熱心街坊通知義工，說在不同的地點見到疑是Stanley的狗狗，義工趕到現場卻屢次撲空。近日再有街坊向義工通報，在某村落連續數晚見到戴着藍頸圈的小狗，在村口的垃圾房摷垃圾食，街坊嘗試靠近，狗狗便嚇得逃跑。「這可能是Stanley，我們這幾天會到現場查看。街坊說會幫忙放置狗糧，希望吸引狗狗再來。」Mimi感激每位街坊的幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223646_a1fd7c5c93ff520cce1059f85372be80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223646_a1fd7c5c93ff520cce1059f85372be80.jpg&h=727c5911&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223808_ef6e73175a7de987030f20c55e266ea6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223808_ef6e73175a7de987030f20c55e266ea6.jpg&h=e3e702d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223649_8a58778ec0c51a9e7d166ecf84964caa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223649_8a58778ec0c51a9e7d166ecf84964caa.jpg&h=4788ac07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不設限期不放棄<br />\n<br />\n然而一次又次的撲空，會否令義工失望放棄？「我們曾試過花了四、五個月才找到失犬。這次我們也不會設尋犬限期，要是設限便等如有放棄的時間，放棄就不再有希望&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n時間不等人，Stanley的媽媽前兩天已經隨新主人飛到法國定居了，義工到機場送別狗媽媽。「雖然不知道牠是否聽得懂，但義工跟狗媽媽說，我們一定會繼續尋找Stanley。」Mimi呼籲如市民見到Stanley的蹤影，可透過「走失協尋(狗/貓)香港 LOST AND FOUND (DOG &amp; CAT) HONG KONG」群組，與義工聯絡。"},{"pid":"6522050a794e06d0c2690629dab857e257dd7fa7","tid":527369,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"元朗巴打幫手留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/224000_34009ba4dfd8b563bd003fd85ea1afbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F224000_34009ba4dfd8b563bd003fd85ea1afbe.jpg&h=2a8b169f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04e6cb81ad6aa2a864f7734af36c02dda96c92c3","tid":527369,"uid":67500,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:42:38.000Z","msg":"有狗帶都走得甩，學人養狗，豬兜"},{"pid":"b235cd2af113f45b2fdace332dbdc6fed7df2b06","tid":527369,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"加油hkdr既義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69851bb902eccf7d699753cc2e769702f9793f3","tid":527369,"uid":24976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T12:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d3e58cdabf58a75c46377ed95c9694718a2b12","tid":527369,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92d355770c084c4b6c55e6e2d60357b542d00426","tid":527369,"uid":49102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"天氣凍 走失狗 元朗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93243bde76ccb7e56cea569bb137ebbab5233be","tid":527369,"uid":24976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:17:49.000Z","msg":"咁都可以俾隻狗走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c003fcef5d81ea4eec6cbfff84ba13f2a0f2ecc","tid":527369,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ef1a017356ac54712b5dfc476873a566ca2685f","tid":527369,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"Stanley只有8個人大<br />\n<br />\n咁撚大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7e092537e2477f0e10b18447dfa6f731ccd3c0","tid":527369,"uid":167124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:01:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbee41553ea785b7370d1d0b97858a2197e5104c","tid":527369,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f237653b61f8cc23b3dc0402993c51ef3197035","tid":527369,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:58:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97e1b24420e8d9be481a1b95e2757de3f66c7dab","tid":527369,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"咁都走得失真係好撚on9"}]}